    "In the first prompt in this phase, it is suggested to ask ChatGPT for any additional information required to produce the results.",
    "Once again, this step can be done multiple times (Initial Prompt -Additional Information -Refined Results) until the user is satisfied with the course assessment methods.",
    "Once the assessment is concluded, the user can ask Chat-GPT to regenerate the course learning outcomes to better align with the assessment methods.",
    "In addition, the user can request ChatGPT to suggest rubrics for the assessments or questions for quizzes, assignments, or final exams.",
    "It is important to reinforce that in this phase, the role of the instructor's expertise is paramount."
